-- Sistema shares jump after reports chairman released, MICEX index higher
-- 
-- Fri Sep 19, 2014 09:34AM EDT
-- None



MOSCOW, Sept 19 (Reuters) - Shares in Russia's Sistema <AFKS.MM> rose strongly on Friday afternoon, and Russia's rouble-denominated MICEX index <.MCX> also jumped, after news reports that its chairman had been released from house arrest.

